Use the standard library
This is how to total_match of lst1 and lst2:
  Remember that matches is []
  Do this lst1's length times:
    Remember that i is diff of lst1's length and 1
    Decrease i by diff of lst1's length and lst1's length
    Remember that word is item i in lst1
    When word is in lst2, then:
      Add matches to word
    End when
  End do
  The answer is matches
